OL,3,CCommunity unites after race attack on
OL,4,Cchurch
OL,6,FPolice said two men used an angle-
OL,7,Fgrinder to cut a hole in the shutters
OL,8,Fof the Templemore Street church
OL,9,Fbuilding before throwing a flammable
OL,10,Fsubstance inside and lighting it.
OL,12,FThey fled when they triggered an
OL,13,Falarm. This happened around 9.30pm on
OL,14,FTuesday.
OL,16,FPolice are treating the incident as a
OL,17,Fracially motivated hate crime and have
OL,18,Fappealed for information.
