OL,3,CCommunity unites after race attack on
OL,4,Cchurch
OL,6,FIt is the latest in a series of racist
OL,7,Fincidents across the city in recent
OL,8,Fweeks.
OL,10,FRev Sammy Robinson, Chair of the East
OL,11,FBelfast Churches Network, said: "We
OL,12,Funequivocally condemn the arson attack
OL,13,Fon the Universal Church of the Kingdom
OL,14,Fof God (UCKG) HelpCentre last night.
OL,16,F"Let us be clear; racism has no place
OL,17,Fin our community.
