OL,6,F"We are deeply saddened that this has
OL,7,Fhappened, especially to a church and
OL,8,Forganisation which seeks to help
OL,9,Fpeople regardless of race or creed
OL,10,Fhere in east Belfast.
OL,12,F"The action of a few will not be
OL,13,Fallowed to tarnish the good name of
OL,14,Fordinary, every day people of east
OL,15,FBelfast who would stand with us in
OL,16,Fcondemning this attack.
