OL,6,F"We would implore anyone with any
OL,7,Finformation to cooperate with the
OL,8,Fpolice in their investigation, and we
OL,9,Fsend our unwavering support, prayers
OL,10,Fand love to those involved in UCKG
OL,11,FHelpCentre Belfast.
OL,13,FThe church, first founded in Brazil in
OL,14,F1977, has congregations across the
OL,15,Fworld, including 45 in the UK. It has
OL,16,Fbeen present in Northern Ireland since
OL,17,F2012 and at the site on Templemore
OL,18,FStreet since 2018. Its congregation
OL,19,Fhas been described as diverse.
