OL,3,CCommunity unites after race attack on
OL,4,Cchurch
OL,6,FOn Wednesday morning, workmen were at
OL,7,Fthe church assessing damage to the
OL,8,Fbuilding.
OL,10,FRev Mervyn Gibson of the nearby
OL,11,FWestbourne Presbyterian Church
OL,12,Fcondemned the incident, saying all
OL,13,Farson attacks are wrong.
OL,15,F"I condemn it unreservedly," he said.
OL,16,F"If those misguided people who did
OL,17,Fthis did it in the name of racism or
OL,18,Fagainst immigration, it should be
OL,19,Fcondemned.
